      "@context": "http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld",
      "type": "Annotation",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "Dodi li vaani lo haro-eh bashoshanim.\nMi zot olah min hamidbar,\nM'kuteret mor ul'vonah . . .\nLibavtini achoti chalah.\nUri tzafon uvo-i teiman ...\nDODI LI\nMy beloved is mine and I am my beloved's who browses among the lilies.\nWho is this that comes up from the desert, in clouds of myrrh and frankincense?\nYou have captured my heart, my sister, my bride.\nAwake, O north wind, come, O south wind!\n(Song of Songs 2:16; 3:6; 4:9, 16)",
          "language": "en"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-07-14T17:42:22.922Z",
      "creator": {
        "isGuest": true,
        "id": "G2ZvXM_0NibL6AXnYXFI"
      },
      "image_url": "https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2F1d22ad1b-bafa-48a8-bf42-71ae4eb2c142.jp2/898,509,3706,1992/max/0/default.jpg"
    },
    {
      "id": "ffbe3bc0-4718-4814-b4b6-410b446e27e0",
      "target": {
        "source": "mishkan:page:1d22ad1b-bafa-48a8-bf42-71ae4eb2c142",
        "type": "SpecificResource",
        "selector": {
          "type": "SvgSelector",
          "value": "<svg><polygon points=\"3087.2631578947367,2883.1578947368425 3087.2631578947367,2721.0526315789475 829.3684210526312,2807.8947368421054 927.7894736842101,3965.7894736842113 4633.0526315789475,3971.5789473684217 4505.684210526317,3630.0000000000005 3156.7368421052633,3583.684210526316\" /></svg>"
